12 

If  confirmed,  there  would  be  no  more  significant  honor  and  cap-
stone  to  my  career  than  to  serve  as  the  Deputy  Administrator  of 
NOAA, and let me conclude by stating that it is my firm conviction 
that  stewardship  through  public  service  is  a  special  privilege  and 
responsibility. 

If confirmed, I will commit my utmost energies, integrity and de-

votion to serving the American people. 

I  want  to  thank  you  again  for  the  opportunity  to  appear  before 
you  today  and  for  your  consideration  of  my  nomination.  I  stand 
ready to answer your questions, sir. 

