ministration  (NOAA)  and  its  subsidiary  branches;  Weather  Service,  Fisheries 
Service, Ocean Service, Satellite and Data Information Service, and Oceanic and 
Atmospheric  Research  in  support  of  a  $100  million  program  related  to  weather 
